#   DATABASE_URL=postgresql://<DB_USER>:<DB_PASS>@dpg-d6latiua2pns73bu1bk0-a/networldship
# - For local development or external connections use the EXTERNAL hostname (public DNS):
#   EXTERNAL_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://<DB_USER>:<DB_PASS>@dpg-d6latiua2pns73bu1bk0-a.oregon-postgres.render.com/networldship
# Replace <DB_USER> and <DB_PASS> with your credentials. DO NOT commit real secrets to git.

